                <hr />
                <h5 class="text-center text-info">Sheep & Goat rearing Trainings</h5>
                <p class="text-justify">To Create self amploment in rural area of the state. The Corporation is conductings 3 days Sheep & Goat Managment training at our 10 Sheep & Goat developments farms training fees Rs. 500/- at farms and Rs. 2000/- at pune.</p>
                <hr />
